dct_description_sm: Map of the Chinese province Ho-pei showing province boundaries, transportation, communications, water features, missions, passes, the Great Wall and populated places. Relief shown by spot heights. "Southern sheet" and "Northern sheet." Includes a Chinese to English explanation and a list of sources of information. "G.S.G.S. no. 2095." Historic Maps copy imperfect: northern sheet wanting.
dct_creator_sm: Great Britain. War Office. General Staff. Geographical Section
